title: High Speed EDM - Volume 2
description: High Speed EDM - Volume 2 is the second collection of 10 electronic tracks with an overall aggressive mood and fast paced rhythmic sections
longDescription:
Preview the collection on YouTube


High Speed EDM - Volume 2 is a collection of 10 electronic tracks 

featuring raw synthesizers, strong rhythmic sections and motivating 

vibes ideal for challenge, sports and extreme contents. 

The inspiration came from cyberpunk crazyness, modern and iconic 

synthesizers from the 90s, futuristic ambients and bold melodies, delivering 

all the energy you need in your projects.

The package includes multiple loops, edit versions, intros and outros for all your editing needs.


Cyber Nights: Full length (01:39), 9 Loops, 3 Edits, Intro&Outro

Electric Freedom: Full length (01:32), 7 Loops, 3 Edits, Intro&Outro

Fast Charge Life: Full length (01:28), 8 Loops, 3 Edits, Intro&Outro

Game of Tron: Full length (04:00), 13 Loops, 3 Edits, Intro&Outro

High Speed Tech: Full length (02:05), 13 Loops, 3 Edits, Intro&Outro

I Should Have Known: Full length (02:58), 15 Loops, 3 Edits, 1 Intro, 2 Outro

  • I Should Have Known (No Pause): Full length (01:49), 1 Loop (01:42)

I Wanna Know: Full length (01:47), 11 Loops, 2 Edits, Intro&Outro

Shifted Dreams: Full length (02:09), 7 Loops, 2 Edits, Intro&Outro

Speed Burns: Full length (01:38), 10 Loops, 3 Edits, Intro&Outro

Synth Highway: Full length (01:14), 9 Loops, 3 Edits, Intro&Outro


Take a look: Total Game Music Collection - 500 High Quality music themes ideal for any game!

This pack is produced by Luca Tomassini a composer with more than 20 years of expertise in music production with multiple TV, feature films and multimedia placements.
